task.summary: Default task
Adding new Android Studio project files
- Updated for latestest BoofCV * tested and it appears to work
- updated fiducial so that you can add new ones by taking pictures - fixed bug in fiducial detector that was making it run very slow
- Binary Image: Added thin operator - Added a slider to the blur activity
- When not in use seekbar is dimmed for thresholding
- added motion detection
- finished black polygon detector
- tweaks
- library help
- added delete to fiducial image library
added text showing there are no fiducials in library fixed bug where fiducial detection didn't resume when leaving help
- final for BoofCV v0.19 - app version 1.6
- Calibration shows a preview of the target you're detecting
- Added calibration fiducials to fiducial menu
- updated for latest version of BoofCV
- updated for latest version of BoofCV - fixed issues with black polygon detector * added button for concave
- fixed scale-space feature detector line size
- improvements to fiducial activities
- fixed and improved contour shape fitting activity
